{"TopicId":174975,"ForumId":98,"TopicTitle":"2001 - A Space Mission Pack - Presented by Shadowzone \u0026amp; Scott Manley","CreatedByName":"illectro","CreatedById":763,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T14:41:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"illectro","CreatedById":763,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T14:41:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHullo! Both myself and Shadowzone had the idea to recreate bits of 2001 in playable form, so for the last few weeks I\u0027ve tried to make precision landing and docking missions based around Space Station V, The Orion Shuttle, The Aries 1B, The Munbus, Klavius Base and TMA-1. While Shadowzone put together a stunning kerbalized version of Discovery One and the maintenance pods. All of these have fully scripted missions with dialogue that references the movie, while letting you actually try landing a nuclear powered shuttle on a small landing pad on the Mun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause the vessels are stock there\u0027s a lot of compromises made. The Orion is tiny because it needs to fit inside the space station, which makes it smaller than the Mun Bus where the priority was to make it look like the original model. But the ships never share a scene so the scaling isn\u0027t noticeable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso the space station doesn\u0027t spin, maybe a future version of Making History will let us do that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload the zipfile here:::\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GBB4pl1rUCV4pjqTwwR7prp1rYWirCMV\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=1GBB4pl1rUCV4pjqTwwR7prp1rYWirCMV\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022eUBqskv.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022583\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/eUBqskv.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qjc5pIz.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022568\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qjc5pIz.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022q08PfwG.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022604\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/q08PfwG.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022930\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022z20a9Qz.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022604\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/z20a9Qz.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022930\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00229XqoM2l.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022604\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/9XqoM2l.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022930\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222EIIR84.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022583\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2EIIR84.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T14:53:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh my god this\u00A0looks awesome and made by a rather awesome team... looks without a doubt absolutly well and timeconsuming work...\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe depicted crafts look so authentic as they could ever be... wow...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nGoing to dl this when i fixed and tested my own remake...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-15T14:53:21Z\u0022 title=\u002205/15/2018 02:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 15, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Mikki\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pkmniako","CreatedById":138569,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T16:15:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt better have bay doors\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cem\u003EChecks image\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt does! Time for some fun reliving the movie!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mrcarrot","CreatedById":176291,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T17:17:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbsolutely brilliant!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T17:36:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, will be the first time I try a mission. Thanks guys!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nilslorand","CreatedById":186824,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T17:37:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoly excrements!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am impressed!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat work guys\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShadowZone","CreatedById":112420,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T21:01:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy I could contribute to this. Hope you guys enjoy the missions!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pehvbot","CreatedById":182810,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T23:27:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223379270\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526400945\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022138569\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pkmniako\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Pkmniako said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt better have bay doors\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cem\u003EChecks image\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt does! Time for some fun reliving the movie!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Open the pod bay doors KAL\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-15T23:28:27Z\u0022 title=\u002205/15/2018 11:28  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 15, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Pehvbot\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Edup text in post, post seems wiggy somehow with new interface.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T00:26:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it\u0027s all stock??? Wow, I have to give this a try!!!\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T18:37:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just played the first three missions and i had the most epic dockingmaneuver in my life\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E... followed by\u00A0one of the most epic crashes in my life\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u00A0(on the surface of m\u00FCn, and not the million ton megastation... wow...)\u003Cbr\u003E\nTruely awesome until now...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-16T18:37:26Z\u0022 title=\u002205/16/2018 06:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 16, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Mikki\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nansuchao","CreatedById":135151,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T18:47:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will start a YT serie on this, if you allow that, obviously giving credit to the mission\u0027s creators.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kBob","CreatedById":102132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T21:04:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea, I always wanted to recreate Rendezvous with Rama, but this looks like a lot of fun too!\u00A0 Have to pick up this DLC soon so I can imagine myself participating in the future of space flight (in 2001, oh well the future isn\u0027t easy to predict).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T22:05:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526504673\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kBob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, kBob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea, I always wanted to recreate Rendezvous with Rama, but this looks like a lot of fun too!\u00A0 Have to pick up this DLC soon so I can imagine myself participating in the future of space flight (in 2001, oh well the future isn\u0027t easy to predict).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuilding a full scaled Rama will be a hell of a challenge, even scaling it down to Kerbals! o.O\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kBob","CreatedById":102132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T22:13:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526508328\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuilding a full scaled Rama will be a hell of a challenge, even scaling it down to Kerbals! o.O\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yeah,\u00A0 have to be scaled down,\u00A0 it was 50km\u00A0long--well beyond the physics range of KSP.\u00A0 But if they add rotation to the ability of the mission builder (as mentioned in \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E) it would be interesting see if the challenges of landing dead center on the end of a rotating cylinder could be simulated.\u00A0 There was also the fun of trying to intercept an object moving at high speeds through the solar system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T23:14:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526508803\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kBob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, kBob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yeah,\u00A0 have to be scaled down,\u00A0 it was 50km\u00A0long--well beyond the physics range of KSP. \u00A0[...] There was also the fun of trying to intercept an object moving at high speeds through the solar system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t make it as a vessel, make it an \u0022asteroid\u0022 or even a \u0022planet\u0022\u00A0:-)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"illectro","CreatedById":763,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T23:37:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526508803\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kBob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, kBob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yeah,\u00A0 have to be scaled down,\u00A0 it was 50km\u00A0long--well beyond the physics range of KSP.\u00A0 But if they add rotation to the ability of the mission builder (as mentioned in \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E) it would be interesting see if the challenges of landing dead center on the end of a rotating cylinder could be simulated.\u00A0 There was also the fun of trying to intercept an object moving at high speeds through the solar system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did a livestream where I was able to make kerbin spin so fast that things fell up, so I used kerbal konstructs to\u00A0 place an inverted runway and land on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, make a tiny planet with almost no mass, but spinning at the correct speed. then surround it with some constructs to be the walls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShame you can\u0027t walk on them because up is down etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-19T22:47:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThought about a book version?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptus","CreatedById":186674,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-21T17:56:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5-star work gentlemen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI finished first 3 missions\u00A0and now we are en route to Jool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe launch, the docking, and the Mun sequences are some of the best experiences I\u0027ve had in KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBack to my career game now, where I have a fleet of ships approaching Jool for the first time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to experience Jool \u0026amp; Laythe in my career game first, then I\u0027ll be back to finish the story.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers \u0026amp; fly safe!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pretorian28715","CreatedById":175947,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T17:40:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk my list to try later too.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T04:18:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoly. Cow.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScott Manley is on the forums?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EOh meh gawd.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EOn a side note, what the heck does \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/763-illectro/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022763\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/763-illectro/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@illectro\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0mean?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-07T04:18:44Z\u0022 title=\u002206/07/2018 04:18  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 7, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Lo Var Lachland\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}